title: 25 MIN STRONG YOGA & STRETCH - Full Body, Low Impact Home Workout - No Equipment, No Repeats
description:
Try this new STRONG YOGA inspired stretch routine to help you increase your mobility and flexibility. I hope you enjoy doing regular mobility sessions and feel super relaxed at the end of this one. No expectations, just follow along! Remember: your body deserves some extra love on your rest days ❤️

♡ Sign up to my Grow with Anna APP: https://growwithanna.page.link/GetGrowNow

▸ Level: All Levels (Low Impact)
▸ Time: 25 Mins
▸ Equipment: No Equipment
▸ Structure: 50 sec on, 10 sec off

Please remember that we are all different and that you can make this your own workout ♡ Take a longer break when you need to.
